Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1100
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set CursorBlink false

Hide
Type "alias arbor=/Users/nick/claude-memory/codepalace/target/release/arbor"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "cd /Users/nick/claude-memory/codepalace"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "# Index a project and see its architecture"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "arbor . --cli | head -10"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type ""
Enter
Type "# Token-optimized compact view"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "arbor . --compact | head -25"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 2s
